      "date": "2026-01-23 17:31:08.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Published edit on patch set 1.\n\nOutdated Votes:\n* Code-Review-1 (copy condition: \"changekind:NO_CHANGE OR changekind:NO_CODE_CHANGE OR changekind:TRIVIAL_REBASE OR is:MIN\")\n",
